OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlue badges may be rejected
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin Europe, drivers warned  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disabled drivers are being warned that 
OL,6, their blue badges may not be accepted  
OL,7, in popular European holiday            
OL,8, destinations this summer due to Brexit.
OL,10,FMinisters are negotiating the status of
OL,11,Fthe badges - which were recognised when
OL,12,Fthe UK was in the EU - with 11 nations.
OL,14,FFrance, Spain, Portugal, Greece and    
OL,15,FItaly are among those "undecided" on   
OL,16,Frecognising the discs, which help      
OL,17,Fpeople park closer to a destination.   
OL,19,FThe AA said keeping blue badge users in
OL,20,F"limbo" was "simply unacceptable".     
